data_table.description: Multiplexed Immunoassay Panel 8 (SABRe Project 2), Offspring Cohort Exam 7, Generation 3 Cohort Exam 1. This is the eighth in a series of immunoassay panels done on the same group of participants (Offspring Exam 7 and Gen 3 Exam 1). To get a full set of all the immunoassays done, please combine the following datasets: l_mpimn01_2005_m_0692s, l_mpimn02_2005_m_0693s, l_mpimn03_2005_m_0694s, l_mpimn04_2005_m_0757s, l_mpimn05_2005_m_0758s, l_mpimn06_2005_m_0792s, l_mpimn07_2005_m_0802s, and l_mpimn08_2005_m_0836s.

variable.name: igfbp1
variable.description: Insulin-like growth factor-binding protein 1 (sample type: plasma)
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for IGFBP1 is 979 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 733000 pg/mL. IGFBP1 values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use IGFBP1_I to see what records are below and above these limits. IGFBP1 values were set to unknown if IGFBP1_CV was greater than or equal to 17.4 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 21.0 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.comment: IGFBP1_CV values were set to unknown if IGFBP1_CV was greater than or equal to 17.4 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 21.0 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).
